== 電影制作 ==
=== 发展 ===
这部影片的发行由于受到2010年米高梅财务危机的影响而延期至2010年12月21日才重新提上日程，2011年1月，米高梅宣布影片的发行日期定在2012年11月9日，比原来预定的发行日期推迟了近一年。米高梅与索尼影视宣布该片在[[英国|英国]]和[[爱尔兰|爱尔兰]]的上映日期提前至2012年10月26日，比美国提前2周<ref>{{cite press release | title = MGM and Sony Pictures Entertainment Announce UK Release Date for Bond 23 | url = http://www.mgm.com/#/news/8 | publisher = [[Metro-Goldwyn-Mayer|Metro-Goldwyn-Mayer]] | accessdate = 2013-01-08 | date = 2011-06-01 | archivedate = 2012-12-06 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121206140638/http://mgm.com/#/news/8 }}</ref>。影片的整体预算估計約位在1.5亿美元<ref>{{cite news | last = Sizemore | first = Charles | title = Bond Investing. James Bond Investing | work = [[Forbes|Forbes]] | date = 2012-10-10 | url = http://www.forbes.com/sites/moneybuilder/2012/10/10/bond-investing-james-bond-investing | accessdate = 2012-11-16 | archivedate = 2012-11-17 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121117111938/http://www.forbes.com/sites/moneybuilder/2012/10/10/bond-investing-james-bond-investing/ }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | last = Smith | first = Grady | title = Box office update: 'Skyfall' blazes past $100 million internationally | work = [[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]] | date = 2012-11-01 | url = http://insidemovies.ew.com/2012/11/01/skyfall-smashes-100-million/ | accessdate = 2012-11-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121117104910/http://insidemovies.ew.com/2012/11/01/skyfall-smashes-100-million/ | archive-date = 2012-11-17 | dead-url = no }}</ref>至2億美元<ref name="bom" />之間，較上一部電影《[[量子危机|量子危机]]》2亿美元的预算有所下降<ref name="200m-Quantum">{{cite news|last=Dawn|first=Randee|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/content_display/film/news/e3ie9098baec9eb95cd02a01aebbd96a968|title='Quantum' is Marc Forster's 007 art film|work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|date=2008-11-11|accessdate=2012-11-02|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081113031127/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/content_display/film/news/e3ie9098baec9eb95cd02a01aebbd96a968|archivedate=2008-11-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 预制 ===

《007量子危機》於2008年上映後，製片人{{link-en|芭芭拉·柏克利|Barbara Broccoli}}評論說，當時未命名的《007：空降危機》可能會延續在《[[007首部曲：皇家夜總會|007首部曲：皇家夜總會]]》中提及並出現在《[[007量子危機|007量子危機]]》裡的量子組織之劇情<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/movies/news/a135633/bond-producer-hints-at-craig-trilogy.html |title=Bond producer hints at Craig trilogy |last1= |first1= |last2= |first2= |date=2008-11-15 |publisher=Digital Spy |accessdate=2013-05-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131230233728/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/movies/news/a135633/bond-producer-hints-at-craig-trilogy.html |archive-date=2013-12-30 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。最終，《007：空降危機》將會是部獨立電影。

2011年8月，許多新聞網站開始轉貼[[塞爾維亞|塞爾維亞]]報紙《Blic》中傳聞占士邦第23部電影，將名為「Carte Blanche」，改編自[[傑佛瑞·迪佛|傑佛瑞·迪佛]]的一本續作小說<ref>{{cite web|title=Serbian to play cello in Bond movie|url=http://english.blic.rs/Culture-Showbiz/7958/Serbian-to-play-cello-in-Bond-movie|publisher=Blic Online|accessdate=2011-08-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110831154105/http://english.blic.rs/Culture-Showbiz/7958/Serbian-to-play-cello-in-Bond-movie|archive-date=2011-08-31|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。8月30日，EON製作公司正式否認任何電影與「Carte Blanche」的聯繫，並指出「新電影不會叫做『Carte Blanche』，也不會是改編自[[傑佛瑞·迪佛|傑佛瑞·迪佛]]的書。」<ref>{{cite web|first=Colin|last=Simpson|title=Bond makers deny online title rumours|url=http://www.thenational.ae/news/uae-news/bond-makers-deny-online-title-rumours|work={{link-en|全國報|The National (Abu Dhabi)|The National}}|date=2011-08-31|accessdate=2012-12-11|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6CpbGNRSM?url=http://www.thenational.ae/news/uae-news/bond-makers-deny-online-title-rumours|archivedate=2012-12-11|deadurl=no}}</ref>2011年10月3日，註冊了包含「jamesbond-skyfall.com」與「skyfallthefilm.com」等網路域名，據報導，這些網域由[[米高梅公司|米高梅公司]]與[[索尼影視娛樂|索尼影視娛樂]]公司委託品牌維護機構{{link-en|MarkMonitor|MarkMonitor}}登記。此舉讓媒體揣測，新電影將命名為「Skyfall」。但這些報導在當時並未為EON製作公司、索尼或者米高梅所證實<ref>{{cite news|last=Thompson|first=Paul|title=007 now has a name! The new troubled James Bond film will be called Skyfall|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2046172/James-Bond-23-title-revealed-Skyfall.html|accessdate=2011-10-08|newspaper=[[Daily_Mail|Daily Mail]]|date=2011-10-07|location=London|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111007223531/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2046172/James-Bond-23-title-revealed-Skyfall.html|archive-date=2011-10-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在11月的一場記者會中，聯合製片人芭芭拉·柏克利證實了本片名為「Skyfall」，並解釋此標題「包含了一些在電影中想表達的情感脈絡」<ref>{{cite web|last=Reynolds|first=Simon|title=James Bond 23 press conference: Daniel Craig on 'Skyfall' – video|url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/movies/news/a348799/james-bond-23-press-conference-daniel-craig-on-skyfall.html|publisher=[[Digital_Spy|Digital Spy]]|accessdate=2013-01-08|date=2011-11-03}}</ref>。

