}}</ref>，她管理[[军情六处|军情六处]]的能力在片中被反复质疑，最终面对公众质询。

[[哈维尔·巴登|哈维尔·巴登]]在片中饰演大反派席尔瓦──一位寻求报复那些他看作要为自己遭背叛负责的网络恐怖主义者<ref>{{cite web|title=The Secrets of Skyfall|url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?feature=player_embedded&v=3ytZBmCIpcM|publisher=Epix (TV channel)|date=2012-10-05|accessdate=2012-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130722213857/http://www.youtube.com/watch?feature=player_embedded&v=3ytZBmCIpcM|archive-date=2013-07-22|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="collin">{{cite news|last=Collin|first=Robbie|authorlink=Robbie Collin|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/film/filmreviews/9604571/Skyfall-James-Bond-review.html|title=Skyfall, James Bond, review|work=[[每日电讯报|每日电讯报]]|location=London|date=2012-10-24|accessdate=2012-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121018065411/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/film/filmreviews/9604571/Skyfall-James-Bond-review.html|archive-date=2012-10-18|dead-url=no}}</ref>。巴登形容席尔瓦“不单是反派”，而克雷格表示邦德和席尔瓦“关系十分重要<ref>{{cite news|title=Daniel Craig Talks 'Bigger, Better' Bond On 'Skyfall' Set|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1682783/skyfall-daniel-craig.jhtml|first=Christina|last=Garibaldi|publisher=MTV|date=2012-04-10|accessdate=2012-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120412195823/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1682783/skyfall-daniel-craig.jhtml|archive-date=2012-04-12|dead-url=no}}</ref> ”。在选角方面，导演[[山姆·曼德斯|山姆·曼德斯]]承认自己努力游说巴登接受角色。曼德斯清楚，角色的潜力被认为是系列中最令人难忘的角色，并创造“观众就邦德电影跳票那么长时间可考虑到的东西<ref>{{cite news|title=Sam Mendes On 'Skyfall' Villain Javier Bardem: 'Silva's Up There With The Greats'|url=http://www.entertainmentwise.com/news/86379/Sam-Mendes-On-Skyfall-Villain-Javier-Bardem-Silvas-Up-There-With-The-Greats|first=Clare|last=Rutter|publisher=Entertainmentwise|date=2012-08-31|accessdate=2012-08-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121128205653/http://www.entertainmentwise.com/news/86379/Sam-Mendes-On-Skyfall-Villain-Javier-Bardem-Silvas-Up-There-With-The-Greats|archive-date=2012-11-28|dead-url=no}}</ref>”。他认为巴登是不分情感色彩的为数不多的演员之一，是当今世界电影里超越剧情功能的事物<ref>{{cite news|title=Javier Bardem is the perfect villain|url=http://www.skynews.com.au/showbiz/article.aspx?id=790029|publisher=[[Sky_News|Sky News]]|date=2012-08-31|accessdate=2012-08-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131231001118/http://www.skynews.com.au/showbiz/article.aspx?id=790029|archive-date=2013-12-31|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在准备角色时，巴登将剧本翻译为母语[[西班牙语|西班牙语]]以便更好融入角色，曼德斯认为这是演员对电影负责的标志<ref>{{cite news|title=Javier Bardem GQ Interview: On 'Skyfall' And Turning Down 'Minority Report'|url=http://news.moviefone.com/2012/09/20/javier-bardem-gq-interview_n_1900880.html|date=2012-09-20|accessdate=2012-09-21|publisher=[[Moviefone|Moviefone]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120923003023/http://news.moviefone.com/2012/09/20/javier-bardem-gq-interview_n_1900880.html|archive-date=2012-09-23|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。曼德斯想让角色拥有独特的视觉，就让巴登染了一头金发<ref>{{cite news|title=Javier Bardem on 'Skyfall': "I don't want to see my funny hair"|url=http://www.digitalspy.com.au/movies/news/a409142/javier-bardem-on-skyfall-i-dont-want-to-see-my-funny-hair.html|first=Paul|last=Martinovic|publisher=Digital Spy|date=2012-09-30|accessdate=2012-10-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121101115736/http://www.digitalspy.com.au/movies/news/a409142/javier-bardem-on-skyfall-i-dont-want-to-see-my-funny-hair.html|archive-date=2012-11-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>，一些评论家观察到角色与[[维基解密|维基解密]]创始人[[朱利安·阿桑奇|朱利安·亞桑傑]]有共同点<ref name="D Tel: Collin" /><ref>{{cite news|last=Gilbey|first=Ryan|title=How James Bond villains reflect the fears and paranoia of their era|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/commentisfree/2012/aug/01/bond-villains-javier-bardem-fears-era?cat=commentisfree&type=article|newspaper=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]|location=London|date=2012-08-01|accessdate=2014-07-18|archive-date=2019-08-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190818150453/https://www.theguardian.com/commentisfree/2012/aug/01/bond-villains-javier-bardem-fears-era?cat=commentisfree&type=article|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="eurweb cast" />。[[貝荷妮絲·瑪赫洛|貝荷妮絲·瑪赫洛]]扮演被席尔瓦救回来，现担任其代表的前澳门[[性交易|性交易]]人赛汶妮<ref>{{cite news|title=Daniel Craig returns as James Bond in new movie Skyfall|url=http://www.smh.com.au/entertainment/movies/daniel-craig-returns-as-james-bond-in-new-movie-skyfall-20111104-1myhm.html|work=[[The_Sydney_Morning_Herald|The Sydney Morning Herald]]|date=2011-11-04|accessdate=2011-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111104133849/http://www.smh.com.au/entertainment/movies/daniel-craig-returns-as-james-bond-in-new-movie-skyfall-20111104-1myhm.html|archive-date=2011-11-04|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Next Bond title revealed: 'Skyfall'|url=http://www.suntimes.com/entertainment/movies/8593232-421/next-bond-title-revealed-skyfall.html|first=Jill|last=Lawless|work=[[Chicago_Sun-Times|Chicago Sun-Times]]|location=Chicago|date=2011-11-04|accessdate=2011-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111105001209/http://www.suntimes.com/entertainment/movies/8593232-421/next-bond-title-revealed-skyfall.html|archive-date=2011-11-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>。玛尔洛将其角色解读为“冷艳且高深莫测，她扮演赛汶妮时从《[[黄金眼|黄金眼]]》的反派珊妮亚·岳纳托（[[芳姬·詹森|芳姬·詹森]]饰）汲取灵感<ref>{{cite web |author=Simon Reynolds and Tom Mansell |url=http://www.digitalspy.com.au/movies/news/a373074/skyfall-berenice-marlohe-talks-bond-girl-severine-video.html |title='Skyfall': Bérénice Marlohe talks Bond girl Severine – video – Movies News |publisher=[[Digital_Spy|Digital Spy]] |date=2012-03-26 |accessdate=2012-04-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121101115721/http://www.digitalspy.com.au/movies/news/a373074/skyfall-berenice-marlohe-talks-bond-girl-severine-video.html |archive-date=2012-11-01 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。」

