外间谍伊芙。尽管媒体炒作哈里斯将饰演钱班霓小姐<ref>{{cite news|last=Child|first=Ben|title=Naomie Harris set to bring Miss Moneypenny back in Bond 23|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/2011/jul/11/naomie-harris-miss-moneypenny-bond-23|accessdate=2012-12-07|newspaper=[[卫报|卫报]]|date=2011-07-11|location=London|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130216052609/http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/2011/jul/11/naomie-harris-miss-moneypenny-bond-23|archive-date=2013-02-16|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Naomie Harris confirmed to play Moneypenny in 'Bond 23'|url=http://www.thegrio.com/entertainment/naomie-harris-confirmed-to-play-moneypenny-in-bond-23.php|publisher=The Grio|accessdate=2012-12-07|date=2011-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120407101810/http://www.thegrio.com/entertainment/naomie-harris-confirmed-to-play-moneypenny-in-bond-23.php|archive-date=2012-04-07|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，但剧组未证实这一点，哈里斯自己出面澄清传闻，指出“伊芙不是遥远的白领<ref name="DM: Moneypenny">{{cite news|last=Wilde|first=Jon|title=The new Bond girls: Naomie Harris and Berenice Marlohe take on 007 in 2012|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/home/moslive/article-2085175/James-Bond-Skyfall-girls-Naomie-Harris-Berenice-Marlohe-007.html|accessdate=2012-12-07|newspaper=[[每日邮报|每日邮报]]|date=2012-01-14|location=London|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120126003517/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/home/moslive/article-2085175/James-Bond-Skyfall-girls-Naomie-Harris-Berenice-Marlohe-007.html|archive-date=2012-01-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>”。照哈里斯所述，夏娃“相信她跟邦德同辈，但她真的是他的鼠辈<ref name="D Tel: Sydney">{{cite news|title=Skyfalls in for James Bond fans as Daniel Craig begins his latest film role on a roof top in London|url=http://www.dailytelegraph.com.au/entertainment/skyfalls-in-for-james-bond-fans-as-daniel-craig-begins-his-latest-film-role-on-a-roof-top-in-london/story-e6frewyr-1226215095786|accessdate=2012-12-07|newspaper=The Daily Telegraph (Australia)|date=2011-12-06|location=Sydney|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130129224332/http://www.dailytelegraph.com.au/entertainment/skyfalls-in-for-james-bond-fans-as-daniel-craig-begins-his-latest-film-role-on-a-roof-top-in-london/story-e6frewyr-1226215095786|archive-date=2013-01-29|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”另一个回归角色Q由[[班·維蕭|班·維蕭]]扮演<ref>{{cite news|title=Ben Whishaw cast as Q in new James Bond film Skyfall|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-15889689|publisher=[[BBC_News_Online|BBC News Online]]|date=2011-11-25|accessdate=2011-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111125173120/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-15889689|archive-date=2011-11-25|dead-url=no}}</ref>。曼德斯最初拒绝证实維蕭的角色<ref name="Screen Int: casting" />，后来说“再引进”这个主意是他出的：“我提出了钱班霓、Q和一个华丽反派的构思，他们同意了。”曼德斯选择[[阿尔伯特·芬尼|阿尔伯特·芬尼]]饰演金凯德<ref>{{cite web|title=Bond Week: From the Set of ''Skyfall''|url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=88991|first=Edward|last=Douglas|publisher=CraveOnline|date=2012-04-16|accessdate=2012-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120419190344/http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=88991|archive-date=2012-04-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>。制片方一度考虑[[史恩·康納萊|史恩·康納萊]]在系列电影50周年的点睛之笔作用，但因为感到康納萊的出现会被视为选角的噱头，使得电影脱离观众，最终没采纳<ref>{{cite news|last=Ryan|first=Mike|title=Sam Mendes, 'Skyfall' Director, on Bringing Humor Back to James Bond & Flirting with the Idea of Casting Sean Connery|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2012/11/04/sam-mendes-skyfall_n_2074239.html|work=The Huffington Post|accessdate=2012-11-28|date=2012-11-05|archivedate=2012-11-29|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6CXh4jwwE?url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2012/11/04/sam-mendes-skyfall_n_2074239.html|deadurl=no}}</ref>。

==== 班底 ====
[[File:Sam_Mendes_2012.jpg|thumb]]于2012年10月巴黎首映礼]]
导演[[山姆·曼德斯|山姆·曼德斯]]在《[[大破量子危机|大破量子危机]]》上映后不久就率先签约本项目，担任[[米高梅公司|米高梅公司]]财务状况不明朗时期的顾问。曼德斯此前跟克雷格在《[[毁灭之路|毁灭之路]]》中有过合作，早在克雷格制作《连绵之雨》时两人有过接触。克雷格提出首次导演邦德电影的话题<ref name="D Tel: Mendes">{{cite news|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/film/jamesbond/9628428/Skyfall-Daniel-Craig-takes-James-Bond-to-another-level.html|first=Vicki|last=Reid|date=2012-10-23|title=Skyfall: Daniel Craig takes James Bond to another level|work=The Daily Telegraph|accessdate=2012-12-31|location=London|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121231072312/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/film/jamesbond/9628428/Skyfall-Daniel-Craig-takes-James-Bond-to-another-level.html|archive-date=2012-12-31|dead-url=no}}</ref>。由于没有邀请，曼德斯最初不愿接受这份工作，也因为克雷格对参与项目的热情，没有立刻拒绝该提议。曼德斯认为克雷格在《[[007：大战皇家赌场|大战皇家赌场]]》的演技，正是他对引领邦德这个主角的感知。他与制片人{{link-en|邁可·G·威爾森|Michael G. Wilson}}和{{link-en|芭芭拉·柏克利|Barbara Broccoli}}看到了电影的早期朝向一番会面后，同意执导电影<ref name="D Tel: Mendes" /> 。媒体猜测，曼德斯曾委托重写剧本，“删除动作戏以突出能获得[[奥斯卡奖|奥斯卡奖]]的‘特色表演’<ref name=TF>{{cite web|last=Chapman|first=Matt|url=http://www.totalfilm.com/news/bond-23-axes-the-action-targets-an-oscar|title=Bond 23 axes the action, targets an Oscar|publisher=[[Total_Film|Total Film]]|location=London|date=2011-10-25|accessdate=2011-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111027194432/http://www.totalfilm.com/news/bond-23-axes-the-action-targets-an-oscar|archive-date=2011-10-27|dead-url=no}}</ref>”。曼德斯否认这一报道，称电影计划中的动作场面是整部戏的灵魂所在<ref name="Conference recording"/>。

[[彼得·摩根|彼得·摩根]]最初委托编写剧本，但因米高梅申请破产，制片搁置而离开项目。尽管离开，摩根后来称最终剧本基于其原本的想法，留下了他认为是重头戏的部分<ref>{{cite web|last1=Reynolds|first1=Simon|authorlink1=Simon Reynolds|last2=Mansell|first2=Tom|url=http://www.digitalspy.com.au/movies/news/a339194/daniel-craigs-james-bond-23-retains-peter-morgan-plot-idea.html|title=Daniel Craig's 'James Bond 23' retains Peter Morgan plot idea – Movies News|publisher=[[Digital_Spy|Digital Spy]]|date=2011-09-08|accessdate=2011-10-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111115143625/http://www.digitalspy.com.au/movies/news/a339194/daniel-craigs-james-bond-23-retains-peter-morgan-plot-idea.html|archive-date=2011-11-15|dead-url=no}}</ref>。曼德斯坚决否认这一说法，称“事实并非如此”，曼德斯同意执导时摩根的剧本已被丢弃<ref name=fji>{{cite news|url=http://www.filmjournal.com/filmjournal/content_display/news-and-features/features/movies/e3i181dbc6afbbcf91d02fec26e3496d7c8|authorlink=Frank Lovece|first=Frank|last=Lovece|title='Skyfall' rising: Oscar winner Sam Mendes guides 007's return to big screen|date=2012-11-06|accessdate=2012-11-10|work=Film Journal International|location=New York|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121110160051/http://www.filmjournal.com/filmjournal/content_display/news-and-features/features/movies/e3i181dbc6afbbcf91d02fec26e3496d7c8|archivedate=2012-11-10|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。最后的剧本是邦德剧本常客{{link-en|尼爾·普維斯|Neal Purvis}}、{{link-en|羅伯·韋德|Robert Wade (screenwriter)}}和{{link-en|約翰·洛根|John Logan (writer)}}所写<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118030077|title=Bond to return with Daniel Craig, Sam Mendes|first=Dave|last=McNary|work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|location=Los Angeles|date=2011-01-11|accessdate=2011-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110114185411/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118030077|archive-date=2011-01-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>。洛根被老相交曼德斯带入该项目，称曼德斯跟编剧“非常合作”，《天幕杀机》是他最难忘的写剧本经历<ref>{{cite news|title=Screenwriter John Logan Talks About His Approach to New James Bond Film ''Skyfall'' and Action Set-Pieces|url=http://collider.com/john-logan-james-bond-skyfall-interview/127574/|first=Adam|last=Chitwood|publisher=Collider.com|date=2011-11-20|accessdate=2011-11-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111121192540/http://collider.com/john-logan-james-bond-skyfall-interview/127574/|archive-date=2011-11-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

此前跟曼德斯是《[[平头日记|平头日记]]》、《[[革命之路|革命之路]]》中有过合作的[[罗杰·狄金斯|罗杰·狄金斯]]担任摄影<ref>{{cite web|last=Heuring|first=David|title='Skyfall:' Double Agents, Data Recording, Roger Deakins|url=http://www.creativeplanetnetwork.com/dv/feature/skyfall-double-agents-data-recording-roger-deakins/60751|publisher=[[NewBay_Media|NewBay Media]]|accessdate=2013-01-08|date=2010-10-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130119171540/http://www.creativeplanetnetwork.com/dv/feature/skyfall-double-agents-data-recording-roger-deakins/60751|archive-date=2013-01-19|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。此前为邦德电影工作过的有<ref name="sonypr" />：丹尼斯·加斯纳担任美术指导，服装设计师为简尼·特米梅，亚历山大·威特担任第二单元导演，加里·鲍威尔和克里斯·考博德担任特技统筹，史蒂夫·贝格负责视觉效果。曾设计《[[量子危机|量子危机]]》片头的平面设计工作室MK12的丹尼尔·克雷曼，再次负责本片片头设计<ref>{{cite news|last=Rosen|first=Christopher|title='Skyfall' Opening Credits Arrive Online (Video)|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2012/11/14/skyfall-opening-credits-video_n_2133058.html|work=The Huffington Post|accessdate=2013-01-08|date=2012-11-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130107082831/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2012/11/14/skyfall-opening-credits-video_n_2133058.html|archive-date=2013-01-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==== 选景 ====
2011年4月，[[山姆·曼德斯|山姆·曼德斯]]与{{link-en|芭芭拉·柏克利|Barbara Broccoli}}前往[[南非|南非]]物色外景<ref>{{cite web|last=Gallagher|first=Brian|title=James Bond 23 Scouting Locations in South Africa|url=http://www.movieweb.com/news/james-bond-23-scouting-locations-in-south-africa|publisher=MovieWeb|date=2011-04-06|access-date=2014-07-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131208010501/http://www.movieweb.com/news/james-bond-23-scouting-locations-in-south-africa|archive-date=2013-12-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>。随着电影8月份预制，有报道透露将在印度开机<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.hindustantimes.com/hollywood/bond-will-be-shot-in-india/story-my9E5l0aE9tcxRBnkDJV2K.html |title=Bond will be shot in India |work=[[印度斯坦時報|印度斯坦時報]] |date=2011-07-30 |accessdate=2020-05-07 |archive-date=2022-01-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220106042740/https://www.hindustantimes.com/hollywood/bond-will-be-shot-in-india/story-my9E5l0aE9tcxRBnkDJV2K.html }}</ref>，片中将出现[[新德里|新德里]]萨罗吉尼纳加尔区<ref name="timesofindia.indiatimes.com">{{cite news |url=http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2011-08-31/india/29949114_1_konkan-railways-railway-ministry-sarojini-nagar-market |title=Latest James Bond film to be shot in India |work=[[The_Times_of_India|The Times of India]] |location=Mumbai |date=2011-08-31 |accessdate=2011-10-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111006185943/http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2011-08-31/india/29949114_1_konkan-railways-railway-ministry-sarojini-nagar-market |archive-date=2011-10-06 |dead-url=no }}</ref>跟[[果阿|果阿]]和[[艾哈迈达巴德|艾哈迈达巴德]]之间的铁路线<ref>{{cite news |url=http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2011-08-22/news-interviews/29914131_1_indian-railways-daniel-craig-shooting |title=Bond going off track in India? |work=[[The_Times_of_India|The Times of India]] |date=2011-08-22 |accessdate=2011-10-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111108155740/http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2011-08-22/news-interviews/29914131_1_indian-railways-daniel-craig-shooting |archive-date=2011-11-08 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。剧组面临着确保有关闭康坎铁路路段权限的并发症，即取得拍摄许可证的类似问题，跟《[[黑暗騎士：黎明昇起|黑暗騎士：黎明昇起]]》和《[[不可能的任務：鬼影行動|不可能的任務：鬼影行動]]》剧组遇到的一样<ref>{{cite news |url=http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2011-08-30/news-interviews/29944760_1_shooting-helicopter-shot-christian-bale |title=Unbonding with India? |work=[[The_Times_of_India|The Times of India]] |location=Mumbai |date=2011-08-30 |accessdate=2011-10-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131206095729/http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2011-08-30/news-interviews/29944760_1_shooting-helicopter-shot-christian-bale |archive-date=2013-12-06 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。邦德剧组最终获得许可，但最终没有于印度拍摄<ref>{{cite news |url=http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2011-09-26/news-interviews/30201085_1_indian-railways-permissions-gauge |title=Bond could have shot |work=[[The_Times_of_India|The Times of India]] |location=Mumbai |date=2011-09-26 |accessdate=2011-10-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131102114149/http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2011-09-26/news-interviews/30201085_1_indian-railways-permissions-gauge |archive-date=2013-11-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 摄制过程 ===
影片拍摄时间原定为133天，实际上用了128天<ref name="Hollywood">{{cite news |title='Skyfall': Hollywood.com Visits the Set of Bond's Latest Mission |url=http://www.hollywood.com/news/Skyfall_James_Bond_Daniel_Craig_Set_Visit_Opening_Action_Scene_Istanbul_Turkey/25962390 |first=Matt |last=Patches |publisher=[[Hollywood.com|Hollywood.com]] |date=2012-05-01 |accessdate=2012-05-02 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20121206015626/http://www.hollywood.com/news/Skyfall_James_Bond_Daniel_Craig_Set_Visit_Opening_Action_Scene_Istanbul_Turkey/25962390 |archive-date=2012-12-06 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="ArriAlexa2">{{cite web |first=Jack |last=Giroux |title=Roger Deakins Makes Bond Cool Again With 'Skyfall' |url=http://www.filmschoolrejects.com/features/roger-deakins-skyfall-jgiro.php |publisher=[[Film_School_Rejects|Film School Rejects]] |date=2012-11-06 |accessdate=2012-12-06 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6ChkgYgBH?url=http://www.filmschoolrejects.com/features/roger-deakins-skyfall-jgiro.php |archivedate=2012-12-06 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，2011年7月于伦敦正式开拍<ref>{{cite web|title=Skyfall: James Bond Press Conference (Full, Unedited)|url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Mi724khLAfE|publisher=[[YouTube|YouTube]]|accessdate=2013-01-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130213130208/http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Mi724khLAfE|archive-date=2013-02-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>，由[[罗杰·迪金斯|罗杰·迪金斯]]使用[[阿莱Alexa|阿莱Alexa]]摄影系统进行拍摄<ref name="ArriAlexa">{{cite web|first=|last=|title=Skyfall set to be the biggest Bond yet|url=http://www.arri.com/news.html?article=1095&cHash=2d1a22f2b0c8d8d913d5a02ad190234e|publisher=ARRI|accessdate=2012-12-06|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6ChlWgK0o?url=http://www.arri.com/news.html?article=1095|archivedate=2012-12-06|deadurl=no}}</ref>，主要在[[伦敦地铁|伦敦地铁]]站<ref>{{cite web|first=Ali|last=Plumb|title=Skyfall London Locations Videoblog Hits|url=http://www.empireonline.com/news/story.asp?NID=34921|publisher=[[Empire_(film_magazine)|Empire]]|date=2012-08-17|accessdate=2012-12-02|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6CbyTB4Ny?url=http://www.empireonline.com/news/story.asp?NID=34921|archivedate=2012-12-02|deadurl=no}}</ref>、[[西史密斯菲尔德大街地下停车场|西史密斯菲尔德大街地下停车场]]、[[萨瑟克区|萨瑟克区]][[英国国家美术馆|国家美术馆]]<ref name="Telegraph">{{cite web|title=Skyfall exclusive: Daniel Craig on filming new Bond in London|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/film/jamesbond/9479861/Skyfall-exclusive-Daniel-Craig-on-filming-new-Bond-in-London-We-got-the-chance-to-shut-down-Whitehall.html|work=[[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Daily Telegraph]]|location=London|date=2012-08-16|accessdate=2012-12-03|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6Cd5edhky?url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/film/jamesbond/9479861/Skyfall-exclusive-Daniel-Craig-on-filming-new-Bond-in-London-We-got-the-chance-to-shut-down-Whitehall.html|archivedate=2012-12-03|deadurl=no}}</ref>、[[白厅|白厅]]、[[国会广场|国会广场]]<ref name="TimeOut">{{cite web|first=|last=|title=Daniel Craig interview|url=http://www.timeout.com/london/feature/3195/daniel-craig-interview|publisher=[[Time_Out_(magazine)|Time Out]]|accessdate=2012-12-02|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6CbtVFfbM?url=http://www.timeout.com/london/feature/3195/daniel-craig-interview|archivedate=2012-12-02|deadurl=yes}}</ref>、 [[查令十字地铁站|查令十字地铁站]]<ref name="DailyMail">{{cite news|first=Sarah|last=Bull|title=Bond arrives in ... Bognor? Highly-anticipated movie Skyfall gets new shooting locations as producers forced to cut budgets|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2088289/Bond-arrives--Bognor-New-movie-Skyfall-gets-new-shooting-locations-producers-forced-cut-budgets.html|newspaper=[[Daily_Mail|Daily Mail]]|location=London|date=2012-01-19|accessdate=2012-12-02|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6CbsydQTi?url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2088289/Bond-arrives--Bognor-New-movie-Skyfall-gets-new-shooting-locations-producers-forced-cut-budgets.html|archivedate=2012-12-02|deadurl=no}}</ref>、[[格林威治|格林威治]]{{link-en|旧皇家海军学院|Old Royal Naval College}}<ref>{{cite news|title=No, Mr Bond; I expect you to die|url=http://footprintsoflondon.com/archives/749|first=Neil|last=Stephens|publisher=Footprints of London|date=2012-01-05|accessdate=2012-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120116224612/http://footprintsoflondon.com/archives/749|archive-date=2012-01-16|dead-url=yes}}</ref>、[[卡多根广场|卡多根广场]]和[[塔山|塔山]]<ref name="Movie-Locations.com" />等地取景。[[军情六处|军情六处]]地下总部则是[[圣巴塞洛缪医院|圣巴塞洛缪医院]]<ref>{{cite news|first=Georgina|last=Littlejohn|first2=Kirsty|last2=McCormack|title=He's back! Daniel Craig dashes through London brandishing James Bond's trusty Walther PPK handgun as he films more scenes for upcoming film Skyfall|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2095954/Daniel-Craig-dashes-London-brandishing-James-Bonds-trusty-Walther-PPK-handgun-films-scenes-upcoming-film-Skyfall.html|newspaper=[[Daily_Mail|Daily Mail]]|location=London|date=2012-09-07|accessdate=2012-12-02|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6CbtyYTrp?url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2095954/Daniel-Craig-dashes-London-brandishing-James-Bonds-trusty-Walther-PPK-handgun-films-scenes-upcoming-film-Skyfall.html|archivedate=2012-12-02|deadurl=no}}</ref>，其训练场为[[滑铁卢车站|滑铁卢车站]]下的旧维克隧道<ref name="Telegraph" />。Q与邦德的碰头是在美术馆晚间闭馆时拍摄的。片末邦德俯瞰倫敦市容的屋頂是[[白廳|白廳]]55號的{{Link-en|能源與氣候變遷部|Department of Energy and Climate Change}}办公楼<ref name="Movie-Locations.com">{{cite web|title=Film locations for Skyfall (2012)|url=http://www.movie-locations.com/movies/s/Skyfall.html|publisher=The Worldwide Guide To Movie Locations|date=2012-11-27|accessdate=2012-12-05|deadurl=yes|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121106233920/http://www.movie-locations.com/movies/s/Skyfall.html|archive-date=2012-11-06}}</ref><ref name="BizIns" /> 。为了拍摄{{link-en|军情六处总部|SIS Building}}爆炸场景，[[沃克斯豪尔桥|沃克斯豪尔桥]]和{{link-en|米尔班克区|Millbank}}交界处进行了交通管制<ref name="BizIns">{{cite web|first=Kirsten|last=Acuna|title=Take A Tour Inside The Filming Locations of the Latest Bond Film, 'Skyfall'|url=http://www.businessinsider.com/skyfall-filming-locations-2012-10?op=1|publisher=Business Insider|date=2012-10-22|accessdate=2012-12-02|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6CbqvLk8Y?url=http://www.businessinsider.com/skyfall-filming-locations-2012-10?op=1|archivedate=2012-12-02|deadurl=no}}</ref>。与通过大型建筑复制品制作爆炸镜头的[[黑日危机|黑日危机]]所不同的是，片中的爆炸是后期加上去的<ref>{{cite web|last=Failes|first=Ian|title=Bond's boldest adventure yet: ''Skyfall''|url=http://www.fxguide.com/featured/skyfall/|publisher=[[Fxguide|Fxguide]]|accessdate=2013-01-08|date=2012-11-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130114220743/http://www.fxguide.com/featured/skyfall/|archive-date=2013-01-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>。片尾原定于{{link-en|登储城堡|Duntrune Castle}}拍摄<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.dailyrecord.co.uk/news/scottish-news/2011/10/07/goldenaye-scotland-s-oldest-inhabited-castle-to-star-in-next-james-bond-movie-86908-23472704/ |title=Scotland's oldest inhabited castle to star in next James Bond movie |publisher=[[Daily_Record_(Scotland)|Daily Record]] |location=Glasgow |date=2011-09-25 |accessdate=2011-10-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111010015238/http://www.dailyrecord.co.uk/news/scottish-news/2011/10/07/goldenaye-scotland-s-oldest-inhabited-castle-to-star-in-next-james-bond-movie-86908-23472704/ |archive-date=2011-10-10 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但在开拍后不久计划就被取消<ref>{{cite news|title=James Bond movie bosses change mind about filming at Scots castle|url=http://news.stv.tv/scotland/west-central/279878-bond-film-will-not-be-shot-at-scots-castle/|first=Leanna|last=MacLarty|publisher=[[STV_Group_(Scotland)|STV]]|date=2011-11-17|accessdate=2011-11-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111122030819/http://news.stv.tv/scotland/west-central/279878-bond-film-will-not-be-shot-at-scots-castle/|archive-date=2011-11-22|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，由苏格兰{{link-en|格伦科高地|Hankley Common}}代替<ref name="BizIns" /><ref>{{cite news|last=Lefley|first=Jack|title=Blown Skyfall High|newspaper=[[Evening_Standard|Evening Standard]]|date=2012-03-26|location=London|page=11}}</ref> 。据称邦德在[[苏格兰|苏格兰]]的祖屋天幕庄园是用[[胶合板|胶合板]]和[[石膏|石膏]]构筑的立体建筑模型<ref>{{cite news|title=Skyfall's secret lies in the Highlands|newspaper=[[The_Herald_(Glasgow)|The Herald]]|date=2012-10-15|location=Glasgow|page=11}}</ref>。

