摄制组于2012年3月移师土耳其，直到5月6日<ref name="April 2012">{{cite news|title=James Bond film crew to close part of Istanbul|url=http://www.hurriyetdailynews.com/james-bond-film-crew-to-close-part-of-istanbul.aspx?pageID=238&nID=17903&NewsCatID=381|newspaper=[[Hürriyet_Daily_News|Hürriyet Daily News]]|location=Istanbul|date=2012-04-09|accessdate=2012-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120410011357/http://www.hurriyetdailynews.com/james-bond-film-crew-to-close-part-of-istanbul.aspx?pageID=238&nID=17903&NewsCatID=381|archive-date=2012-04-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>，原计划是要在该地拍摄三个月<ref>{{cite news|title=Bond to visit Adana!|url=http://www.sabahenglish.com/Arts/2011/12/26/bond-to-visit-adana|work=[[Sabah_(newspaper)|Sabah English]]|publisher=Ahmet Çalık|date=2011-12-26|accessdate=2012-01-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120426085445/http://www.sabahenglish.com/Arts/2011/12/26/bond-to-visit-adana|archive-date=2012-04-26|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 。影片中的[[伊斯坦布尔|伊斯坦布尔]]郊外取景于[[亚达那|亚达那]]<ref name="Patrice">{{cite news|title=James Bond set-besøg i Adana|language=da|trans_title=On the set of 'Skyfall'|url=http://www.kino.dk/nyheder/2012/04/james-bond-set-besoeg-i-adana|first=Tora|last=Eff|publisher=Kino|date=2012-04-13|accessdate=2012-04-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120415112543/http://www.kino.dk/nyheder/2012/04/james-bond-set-besoeg-i-adana|archive-date=2012-04-15|dead-url=no}}</ref>，在对火车顶打斗场面进行彩排时，一群当地儿童溜进了用于拍摄的铁路专用线而被保安抓获<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.hurriyetdailynews.com/teens-infiltrate-james-bond-set-film-fight-scene-.aspx?pageID=238&nID=16338&NewsCatID=381 |title=CINEMA-TV – Teens infiltrate James Bond set, film fight scene |newspaper=[[Hürriyet_Daily_News|Hürriyet Daily News]] |location=Istanbul |date=2012-03-12 |accessdate=2012-04-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120323224653/http://www.hurriyetdailynews.com/teens-infiltrate-james-bond-set-film-fight-scene-.aspx?pageID=238&nID=16338&NewsCatID=381 |archive-date=2012-03-23 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。电影火车戏的预告片还出现了[[瓦尔达高架桥|瓦尔达高架桥]]，邦德的替身安迪·赖斯特于距地面300英尺高的此处背身落入水中<ref name="BizIns" />。此外，片中火车上的起重机用安全绳绑着。在伊斯坦布尔部分出现的景点还包括：{{link-en|香料集市|Spice Bazaar}}、[[新清真寺_(伊斯坦布尔)|新清真寺]]、{{link-en|土耳其邮政总局|Main Post Office}}、因拍摄而停止迎客的[[君士坦丁堡竞技场|君士坦丁堡竞技场]]和[[大巴扎|大巴扎]]<ref name="April 2012"/>，均于4月杀青。这些地区的商户可以开门，但不准营业，他们将获得750里拉（即418美元）一天的补偿<ref name="April 2012"/>。摩托车屋顶追逐戏让摄制组面临着涉嫌损坏古建筑的批评。但迈克尔·威尔逊否认这些说法，他表示开拍前已派人把部分屋顶拆掉，用复制品代替，待到拍摄结束后就恢复原貌<ref>{{cite news|title=We are careful not to damage cultural values: Bond producer|url=http://www.hurriyetdailynews.com/we-are-careful-not-to-damage-cultural-values-bond-producer.aspx?pageID=238&nID=19016&NewsCatID=381|accessdate=2013-01-08|newspaper=[[Hürriyet_Daily_News|Hürriyet Daily News]]|date=2012-04-23|location=Istanbul|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120425231834/http://www.hurriyetdailynews.com/we-are-careful-not-to-damage-cultural-values-bond-producer.aspx?pageID=238&nID=19016&NewsCatID=381|archive-date=2012-04-25|dead-url=no}}</ref>。摄制组获得业主的同意后，还于[[费特希耶|费特希耶]]卡利伺海滩613片取景<ref name="BizIns" />。

由导演曼德斯证实，[[上海|上海]]等地将出现在影片中<ref name="Conference recording"/>。{{link-en|約翰·洛根|John Logan (writer)}}表示，摄制组故意找了一处跟伦敦风格不同、具有异国情调的取景地，让邦德不太舒服地出现<ref name="BizIns" />。实际上，有许多场面并不在上海取景，如屋顶的游泳池是[[金丝雀码头|金丝雀码头]]的{{link-en|维珍活力|Virgin Active}}游泳池<ref name="Telegraph" /><ref name="BizIns" />，邦德进入的大厦是伦敦第四高楼[[布罗德盖特塔|布罗德盖特塔]]，外部灯光将其打扮成一座写字楼<ref name="BizIns" />。为了拍摄航拍镜头，剧组罕见地得到中国政府批准並借出直升機进行航空拍攝<ref name="BizIns" /> 。邦德碰到反派席尔瓦的澳门金龙赌场内景在{{link-en|松林制片厂|Pinewood}}搭建<ref name="BizIns" />，而[[上海浦东国际机场|上海浦东国际机场]]则在[[雅士谷赛马场|雅士谷赛马场]]搭景<ref>{{cite news|last=Maddox|first=Garry|title=James Bond's Britain|url=http://www.theage.com.au/travel/james-bonds-britain-20121123-29xbs.html|accessdate=2012-11-30|newspaper=[[The_Age|The Age]]|date=2012-11-25|location=Melbourne|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121202221134/http://www.theage.com.au/travel/james-bonds-britain-20121123-29xbs.html|archive-date=2012-12-02|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Mathieson|first=Amy|title=Ascot racecourse to star in James Bond film|url=http://www.horseandhound.co.uk/news/397/310912.html|publisher=[[Horse_&_Hound|Horse & Hound]]|accessdate=2012-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121012005508/http://www.horseandhound.co.uk/news/397/310912.html|archive-date=2012-10-12|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。在2012年2月1日公布的首张电影剧照中，克雷格正在松林制片厂搭建的一座“位于上海”的摩天大楼中娱乐<ref>{{cite web|title=First official picture from Skyfall revealed|url=http://www.007.com/bond-is-back/|publisher=[[Eon_Productions|Eon Productions]] and [[Metro-Goldwyn-Mayer|Metro-Goldwyn-Mayer]]|accessdate=2012-02-01|date=2012-02-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120201174528/http://www.007.com/bond-is-back/|archive-date=2012-02-01|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

据2012年4月的报道，影片将在[[长崎|长崎]]海岸线上一座名叫[[端島|端島]]的废弃小岛上取景<ref>{{cite news|title=Bond Week: Four New Skyfall Photos!|url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=89081|first=Edward|last=Douglas|publisher=[[CraveOnline|CraveOnline]]|date=2012-04-11|accessdate=2012-04-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120413173820/http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=89081|archive-date=2012-04-13|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title = Skyfall Preview and Pics | url = http://au.movies.ign.com/articles/122/1222743p1.html | publisher = [[IGN|IGN]] | date = 2012-04-12 | accessdate = 2012-04-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120414024810/http://au.movies.ign.com/articles/122/1222743p1.html | archive-date = 2012-04-14 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>，该岛在片中被设置成澳门海岸线上的一座无名小岛。[[山姆·曼德斯|山姆·曼德斯]]解释，该场景其实是一组计算机生成的图像<ref name=newsday>{{cite news | url = http://www.newsday.com/entertainment/movies/skyfall-james-bond-still-stirs-series-principals-1.4198351 | title = 'Skyfall' James Bond still stirs series principals | date = 2012-11-07 | authorlink = Frank Lovece | first = Frank | last = Lovece | work = [[Newsday|Newsday]] | location = New York | archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/6E1016GFL?url=http://www.newsday.com/entertainment/movies/skyfall-james-bond-still-stirs-series-principals-1.4198351 | archivedate = 2013-01-28 | deadurl = no | access-date = 2013-07-29 }}</ref>，摄制组在[[丹尼尔·克雷格|丹尼尔·克雷格]]会见于[[斯德哥尔摩|斯德哥尔摩]]拍摄的电影《[[龍紋身的女孩_(2011年電影)|龙纹身的女孩]]》的瑞典电影制作人Thomas Nordanstad后，选择了端島的地理模型。Nordanstad曾于2002年在该地拍摄名为《端島》的短纪录片，根据克雷格在该岛上所写的大量笔记，导演是在影片上映后才得知这座岛的详细<ref>{{cite web | title = The History of Hashima, the Island in Bond Film "Skyfall" | url = http://www.theworld.org/2012/11/the-history-of-hashima-the-island-in-bond-film-skyfall/ | first = Clark | last = Boyd | publisher = [[The_World_(radio_program)|The World]] | date = 2012-11-23 | accessdate = 2012-12-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121129102737/http://www.theworld.org/2012/11/the-history-of-hashima-the-island-in-bond-film-skyfall/ | archive-date = 2012-11-29 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

影片后来转制[[IMAX|IMAX]]格式以供在巨幕影院放映。迪金斯原本不清楚影片将以IMAX形式发行，直到他后来决定用[[阿莱Alexa|阿莱Alexa]]摄影机拍摄<ref name="ArriAlexa" />。在进行画面试验时，色彩的不完美展现，使其产生不快。在进一步探讨IMAX系统，了解到IMAX公司专用的[[IMAX#IMAX_DMR_（数字媒体复修）|数字媒体复修]]技术后，迪金斯发现他并没有使用该功能进行测试，从而平息他对该格式的怀疑<ref name="ArriAlexa" />。

=== 配樂 ===
