本片在全球共赢得11亿美元的票房<ref name="bom" />，为索尼影业全球范围内最卖座的电影，是[[2012年电影|2012年票房第二高影片]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=97911|title=Box Office Results: Skyfall Becomes Sony's Highest-Grossing Film Ever|publisher=CraveOnline|date=2012-12-17|accessdate=2012-12-19|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6E4i2xYUC?url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=97911|archivedate=2013-01-31|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=2012 Worldwide Grosses|url=http://boxofficemojo.com/yearly/chart/?view2=worldwide&yr=2012&p=.htm|publisher=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]|accessdate=2012-12-31|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190611022729/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/yearly/chart/?view2=worldwide&yr=2012&p=.htm|archivedate=2019-06-11|deadurl=no}}</ref>。上映首周末，本片就从25个市场赚得8060万美元<ref name="BOM-over1">{{cite web|last=Subers|first=Ray|title=Around-the-World Roundup: Bond is Back with $80.6 Million Overseas|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3555|date=2012-11-19|publisher=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]|accessdate=2012-11-28|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6E4iOzitX?url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3555|archivedate=2013-01-31|deadurl=no}}</ref>。在英国，本片首周票房2010万英镑，仅次于《[[哈利波特：死神的聖物Ⅱ|哈利波特：死神的聖物Ⅱ]]》，屈居首周周末票房榜第二位<ref>{{cite news|last=Child|first=Ben|title=Skyfall smashes UK box office records|work=[[卫报|卫报]]|location=伦敦|date=2012-10-29|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/2012/oct/29/skyfall-uk-box-office-records-james-bond|accessdate=2012-11-29|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6E4iRvAJv?url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/2012/oct/29/skyfall-uk-box-office-records-james-bond|archivedate=2013-01-31|deadurl=no}}</ref>，是仅次于《[[黑暗騎士：黎明昇起|黑暗騎士：黎明昇起]]》的票房第二高IMAX影片<ref name="BOM-over1"/>。影片一周内最高票房记录为3720万英镑，超越《死亡圣器Ⅱ》保有的记录<ref>{{cite news|last=Child|first=Ben|title=Skyfall breaks UK seven-day box-office record|work=[[卫报|卫报]]|location=伦敦|date=2012-11-05|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/2012/nov/05/skyfall-uk-box-office-record|accessdate=2012-11-29|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6E4iapsJK?url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/2012/nov/05/skyfall-uk-box-office-record|archivedate=2013-01-31|deadurl=no}}</ref>。截至2012年11月9日，本片斩获5700万英镑，超越《黎明昇起》成为2012年票房最高电影，也成为在英国最卖座的詹姆斯·邦德电影<ref>{{cite news|last=Child|first=Ben|title=Skyfall becomes this year's biggest seller at the UK box office|work=[[卫报|卫报]]|location=伦敦|date=2012-11-09|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/2012/nov/09/skyfall-biggest-seller-box-office|accessdate=2012-11-29|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6E4ijYHl7?url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/2012/nov/09/skyfall-biggest-seller-box-office|archivedate=2013-01-31|deadurl=no}}</ref>。英国上映40天后，本片票房维持在9428万英镑，超越《[[阿凡达|阿凡达]]》的9403万英镑，成为英国票房最高的电影<ref>{{cite news|last=Gant|first=Charles|title=Skyfall windfall is UK box office's biggest ever|work=[[卫报|卫报]]|location=伦敦|date=2012-12-05|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/filmblog/2012/dec/05/skyfall-uk-box-office|accessdate=2012-12-05|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6E4in0Ay5?url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/filmblog/2012/dec/05/skyfall-uk-box-office|archivedate=2013-01-31|deadurl=no}}</ref>。2012年12月30日，该片成为首部票房破1亿美元的电影（1.61亿英镑）<ref name="BOUK100First">{{cite news |last=McClintock |first=Pamela |title=Box Office Milestone: Daniel Craig's 'Skyfall' Crosses $1 Billion Worldwide |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/james-bonds-skyfall-1-billion-407126 |date=2012-12-30 |work=好莱坞记者 |accessdate=2012-12-30 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6DIqjCfIA?url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/james-bonds-skyfall-1-billion-407126 |archivedate=2012-12-30 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。本片斩获的票房过1亿，曾在[[第七號情報員|第1部]]和[[雷霆殺機|第17部007电影]]出现过，相当于《[[霹靂彈|霹靂彈]]》赚取的10.47亿美元算入通胀调整<ref>{{cite web|title=All Time Worldwide Box Office Grosses|publisher=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/alltime/world|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130227031544/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/alltime/world|archivedate=2013-02-27|acce