* {{cite news|last=French|first=Philip|title=Skyfall – review|newspaper=[[观察家报|观察家报]]|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/2012/oct/28/skyfall-james-bond-review|date=2012-10-28|authorlink=Philip French|location=London|page=32|access-date=2014-08-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130629052058/http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/2012/oct/28/skyfall-james-bond-review|archive-date=2013-06-29|dead-url=no}}
* {{cite web |first=Daniel |last=Krupa |url=http://uk.ign.com/articles/2012/10/13/skyfall-review |title=007 Reporting For Duty, Ma'am |publisher=IGN |date=2012-10-12 |accessdate=2012-11-12 |archive-date=2019-08-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190818150449/https://www.ign.com/articles/2012/10/13/skyfall-review |dead-url=no }}
* {{cite news|title=Dial M for the best Bond ever?|newspaper=[[Irish_Independent|Irish Independent]]|date=2012-10-26|location=Dublin}}
* {{cite news|title=Skyfall Has it All|newspaper=每日记事|date=2012-10-16|location=格拉斯哥|pages=50–51}}</ref>。《[[每日电讯报|每日电讯报]]》影评人罗比·科林（Robbie Collin）认为本片“常让人眼花缭乱，总是大胆妄为”，片中的优秀动作场面带有幽默和情感色彩<ref name="D Tel: Collin">{{cite news|last=Collin|first=Robbie|title=007: a superhero for our times; its action scenes are dazzling as ever, but the latest Bond is also full of humour and warmth|url=https://archive.org/details/100daysthatchang0000unse|newspaper=[[每日电讯报|每日电讯报]]|date=2012-10-26|authorlink=Robbie Collin|location=London|page=[https://archive.org/details/100daysthatchang0000unse/page/33 33]}}</ref>。《[[好莱坞记者|好莱坞记者]]》的托德·麦卡锡（Todd McCarthy）认为本片“明显地扣人心弦，同时还挥舞着幽默的滑稽暗流”，从而称本片“有一定重量并带复杂性<ref name="mccarthy">{{cite news|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/movie/skyfall/review/378796|last=McCarthy|first=Todd|authorlink=Todd McCarthy|title=Skyfall Review Daniel Craig|work=[[好莱坞记者|好莱坞记者]]|date=2012-10-13|accessdate=2012-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121110231004/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/movie/skyfall/review/378796|archive-date=2012-11-10|dead-url=no}}</ref> ”。《[[综艺_(杂志)|综艺杂志]]》的彼得·德波吉（Peter DeBruge）认为本片最大的优势，在于愿意尽可能多地把动作套路集中在表征上，让两者结合，而非单纯吸引观众眼球<ref name="debruge">{{cite news |last=Debruge |first=Peter |url=http://www.variety.com/review/VE1117948556/ |title=Skyfall |work=[[综艺_(杂志)|综艺]] |date=2012-10-13 |accessdate=2012-10-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121017012423/http://www.variety.com/review/VE1117948556/ |archive-date=2012-10-17 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。但《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》影评人马诺哈拉·达吉斯，认为本片卓越继承了“《[[007：大战皇家赌场|大战皇家赌场]]》，“华丽而非古怪，且不断地逐渐低调<ref name="NY Times: Dargis">{{cite news|last=Dargis|first=Manohla|authorlink=Manohla Dargis|title=What a Man! What a Suit!|newspaper=[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]|date=2012-11-07|url=http://movies.nytimes.com/2012/11/08/movies/skyfall-with-daniel-craig-as-james-bond.html|access-date=2014-08-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130530050839/http://movies.nytimes.com/2012/11/08/movies/skyfall-with-daniel-craig-as-james-bond.html|archive-date=2013-05-30|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”《[[帝国_(杂志)|帝国]]》的金·纽曼（Kim Newman）总结本片“融合了几乎你能想到的所有当代邦德形象：冷酷而不做作，尊重传统，但直到目前，严重的刺激使角色相当复杂，有趣的感受近来并不总是显而易见<ref name="Empire-Newman">{{cite web|url=http://www.empireonline.com/reviews/reviewcomplete.asp?FID=137076|title=Skyfall|last=Newman|first=Kim|authorlink=Kim Newman|work=[[帝国_(杂志)|帝国]]|publisher=Bauer Media Group|accessdate=2012-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121024221709/http://www.empireonline.com/reviews/reviewcomplete.asp?FID=137076|archive-date=2012-10-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”《[[芝加哥太阳报|芝加哥太阳报]]》的罗杰·艾伯特（Roger Ebert）给予本片4星满分，称其“感情强烈、欢快，是深受人们喜爱的文化表征的智能化庆典。”《新政治家》的瑞安·吉尔比（Ryan Gilbey）看到“弥漫在电影中的怀旧气息”，称“有时旧路子是最好的<ref name="New State">{{cite news|last=Gilbey|first=Ryan|title=Skyfall—review|newspaper=新政治家|location=London|url=http://www.newstatesman.com/culture/film/2012/10/dial-m-mother-review|date=2012-10-29|issn=1364-7431|access-date=2014-08-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130206082947/http://www.newstatesman.com/culture/film/2012/10/dial-m-mother-review|archive-date=2013-02-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>”。
